title: Cyphers
sinopse:
Ep 1: The grand opening animation trailer for the nation-wide launch of the Korean video game Cyphers.

Ep 2: "Cyphers Episode 1: Feather", fully voiced action-packed animated feature made in 2011. No more were created after this initial one.

Ep 3: The commemorative 5th Anniversary animation trailer for the Korean video game Cyphers.
